uv venv
uv sync

# Lint
ruff check .

# Type check
mypy src/

# Test
pytest

# Build
pygenkit build
```

## Release

```bash
pygenkit release
```

This will:
1. Increment version
2. Update changelog
3. Create git tag
4. Push to GitHub
5. Trigger CI/CD

## CI/CD

| Workflow | Trigger | Action |
|----------|---------|--------|
| CI | PR / push | Ruff, MyPy, Pytest |
| Release | Tag `v*` | PyPI publish + GitHub Release |
| Launchpad | Tag `v*` | Source package + PPA upload |

